		{
			"id":"04884adc989796a4",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"# HH Caldera Mine\nCurio tells you that a Redoran with claims to Caldera has surfaced in Ald-ruhn. You are sent to either convince them to defect to HH or kill them.",
			"styleAttributes":{
				"border":null
			},
