		},
		{
			"id":"6e9d88d7e0160c89",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"# HR Caldera Mine\nLlethri sends you to find new Uveran NPC. Need to convince them that they'll be safe from MT assassins when they make a claim to Caldera.",
